Contribute to the development and capacity building of USAID Takamol networks on the grassroots level, including youth, women, and community-based organizations, with regards to economic empowerment from a gender perspective. This task will include designing community-based initiatives (both online and offline) and community-driven campaigns to promote awareness and advocate for an effective enabling environment to empower women, youth, and communities economically;
